{"tid":2309952,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"去年3.3萬人申良民證增三成 許正宇：不代表移民","createTime":"2020-12-03T02:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T15:36:05.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"712410327d204b05e3373fdfd888d7adab4f7ebf","tid":2309952,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T02:18:01.000Z","msg":"近年不少香港移民海外，一般而言，香港人申請移民時需要向香港警務處申請簽發「良民證」，證明自己沒有犯罪紀錄。財經事務及庫務局局長許正宇今日（2日）在立法會回應議員質詢時表示，去年有3.3萬人申請俗稱「良民證」，較前兩年增約1萬人，但強調申請「良民證」的原因除移民以外，還包括其他因素如海外升學及交換訪問等。他表示，並非所有成功申請者最終可申請移民簽證，認為分析數據時需考慮有關因素。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201202/6OTG4YEDO5EFXNAAFFPW5HO7FA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201202%2F6OTG4YEDO5EFXNAAFFPW5HO7FA%2F&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=045811a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201202%2F6OTG4YEDO5EFXNAAFFPW5HO7FA%2F&h=c53a6e61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201202/6OTG4YEDO5EFXNAAFFPW5HO7FA/</a>"},{"pid":"4e993c8e8f457dad29b8888f73d22f49dd17ba09","tid":2309952,"uid":353063,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"712410327d204b05e3373fdfd888d7adab4f7ebf","tid":2309952,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T02:18:01.000Z","msg":"近年不少香港移民海外，一般而言，香港人申請移民時需要向香港警務處申請簽發「良民證」，證明自己沒有犯罪紀錄。財經事務及庫務局局長許正宇今日（2日）在立法會回應議員質詢時表示，去年有3.3萬人申請俗稱「良民證」，較前兩年增約1萬人，但強調申請「良民證」的原因除移民以外，還包括其他因素如海外升學及交換訪問等。他表示，並非所有成功申請者最終可申請移民簽證，認為分析數據時需考慮有關因素。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201202/6OTG4YEDO5EFXNAAFFPW5HO7FA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201202%2F6OTG4YEDO5EFXNAAFFPW5HO7FA%2F&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=045811a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201202%2F6OTG4YEDO5EFXNAAFFPW5HO7FA